    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The last specific conceptual schemes in the creative process, defining the organization or appearance of a work or creative endeavor; final designs are typically expressed in the finished work.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
